Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:10.55,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.47,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,んっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.13,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:15.63,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,ええっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:16.68,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,なっ
